WEBVTT

00:02.836 --> 00:05.073
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:05.106 --> 00:06.574
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da
Let's go!

00:06.607 --> 00:08.309
♪ We'll be there

00:08.342 --> 00:10.978
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:11.011 --> 00:13.181
♪ Yeah, we'll be there

00:13.214 --> 00:15.249
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:15.283 --> 00:17.585
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:17.618 --> 00:18.919
♪ We'll jump out the bush

00:18.952 --> 00:20.654
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:20.688 --> 00:22.090
♪ We'll be there

00:24.558 --> 00:30.164
