00:30.198 --> 00:33.101
Hey, you guys know why we're
wandering around Koreatown?

00:33.134 --> 00:34.535
Are we getting
some shaved ice?

00:34.568 --> 00:36.204
Ice Bear's ready
for some PC bang.

00:36.237 --> 00:37.405
No, sillies.

00:37.438 --> 00:39.707
We're gonna go relax
at a Korean spa.

00:39.740 --> 00:42.510
Korean spa? Why?
Aren't those things expensive?

00:42.543 --> 00:46.080
Not today, because I found
this incredible coupon

00:46.114 --> 00:47.581
in the trash the other day.

00:47.615 --> 00:50.451
I'll be able to do anything
for practically free.

00:50.484 --> 00:52.386
Free is a very good cost.

00:52.420 --> 00:54.722
Okay.
Oh, I think this is it.

00:54.755 --> 00:56.657
Let's do this.

00:58.559 --> 01:00.728
Grizzly:
Whoa. [ Laughs ]

01:00.761 --> 01:02.096
This place is fancy.

01:02.130 --> 01:04.965
Yeah, it is.
Ann-yo-hase-oh!

01:04.998 --> 01:07.635
[ Speaking Korean ]

01:08.936 --> 01:11.439
Hello.
Welcome to Hill Spa.

01:11.472 --> 01:13.941
Thanks. Ah. We're here for
the Korean spa experience.

01:13.974 --> 01:17.245
[ Clears throat ]
Choose from menu, please.

01:17.278 --> 01:20.881
Whoa, VIP Course?
I'll definitely take that.

01:20.914 --> 01:22.250
'Cause I'm worth it.

01:22.283 --> 01:24.084
Very, very nice choice.

01:24.118 --> 01:25.753
[ Speaking Korean ]

01:25.786 --> 01:27.755
Dude, are you sure
you could afford that?

01:27.788 --> 01:28.722
Pfff, don't worry, man.

01:28.756 --> 01:30.090
-[ Speaking Korean ]
-Huh?

01:30.124 --> 01:32.426
-This way, please.
-Oh. Cool.

01:32.460 --> 01:35.129
Okay, you guys get whatever you
want on the menu. It's on me.

01:35.163 --> 01:38.299
I'm a VIP now, baby.
VIP ju-se-yo.

01:38.332 --> 01:39.767
Welcome to Hill Spa.

01:39.800 --> 01:43.237
Hi, uh, so do you have
anything I could do

01:43.271 --> 01:44.772
to just relax or be alone?

01:44.805 --> 01:47.175
Okay, you can use
the steam room.

01:47.208 --> 01:48.976
Very, very nice.
Thank you.

01:49.009 --> 01:50.278
Ooh, that sounds nice.

01:50.311 --> 01:51.579
Ice Bear doesn't like steam.

01:51.612 --> 01:54.415
You can sleep in the sleep room.
Thank you.

01:54.448 --> 01:56.850
-Ice Bear can only sleep in --
-Thank you.

01:56.884 --> 01:59.253
C'mon, let's go.

01:59.287 --> 02:01.255
[ Humming ]

02:01.289 --> 02:03.023
You look very good.

02:03.056 --> 02:04.292
Aw, thanks, man.

02:04.325 --> 02:06.527
[ Chuckles ] Yeah, boy.

02:07.728 --> 02:11.799
Ooh.
Ooh, ooh, ooh, ahh.

02:11.832 --> 02:14.635
Ahh. Huh? Ooh.

02:14.668 --> 02:18.539
Oh. Oh.
[ Chuckles ] Deluxe.

02:19.807 --> 02:21.275
Ahh.

02:21.309 --> 02:23.977
Yes. Ahh.

02:24.011 --> 02:26.647
[ Moaning ]

02:29.016 --> 02:31.619
Whoa, nice. Nobody's here.

02:31.652 --> 02:33.354
[ Woman speaking Korean ]
Huh?

02:33.387 --> 02:35.323
[ Woman speaking Korean ]

02:35.356 --> 02:39.327
Hmm. Uh, how can I change this
to English?

02:39.360 --> 02:42.830
[ Woman speaking Korean ]

02:42.863 --> 02:44.332
Whoa. What did I do?

02:44.365 --> 02:46.900
Oh. [ Laughs ]

02:46.934 --> 02:49.002
Uh...hmm.

02:50.204 --> 02:51.805
Ahh.

02:51.839 --> 02:53.307
[ Doorknob rattles ]
Huh?

02:53.341 --> 02:55.876
[ Sighs ]

02:58.078 --> 02:59.580
[ Grunts ]

02:59.613 --> 03:01.315
Hi.

03:01.349 --> 03:03.951
Uh, h-hi.

03:06.854 --> 03:09.357
Please don't sit next to me.
Please don't sit next to me.

03:09.390 --> 03:12.993
[ Groaning ]

03:13.026 --> 03:15.996
[ Growls ] Why?

03:16.029 --> 03:17.265
What?

03:17.298 --> 03:19.500
It's Korean candy.

03:19.533 --> 03:21.201
Oh, no, no, no,
I'm full.

03:21.235 --> 03:23.704
I had a big lunch.
So, thanks.

03:26.240 --> 03:28.709
[ Grunts ]

03:28.742 --> 03:31.879
Ugh, I'm not leaving.
I was here first.

03:31.912 --> 03:42.022
♪♪

03:42.055 --> 03:43.624
Hmm.

03:43.657 --> 03:44.558
Hmm.

03:44.592 --> 03:46.594
[ Ping-Pong balls bouncing ]

03:46.627 --> 03:49.463
[ Men grunting,
speaking Korean ]

03:53.934 --> 03:56.770
Hey, there. How's it going?
Wanna give it a try?

03:56.804 --> 03:58.372
Here.

03:58.406 --> 03:59.707
No, no, no, no, no.

03:59.740 --> 04:01.775
This is how you hold it.
First time, huh?

04:01.809 --> 04:03.577
Come.
I'll show you how to play.

04:03.611 --> 04:06.747
All right,
so this is how you hit the ball.

04:06.780 --> 04:09.817
Like this. Easy, huh?
Now you try.

04:11.985 --> 04:14.154
Yeah. Nice.

04:14.187 --> 04:16.056
You're a natural.

04:16.089 --> 04:17.591
[ Chomping ]

04:17.625 --> 04:20.594
Mm. Mm. Ah. Mm.

04:20.628 --> 04:21.829
-Okay...
-Huh?

04:21.862 --> 04:24.498
VIP time is over.
Thank you.

04:24.532 --> 04:26.734
Aw. What? Really?
Boo.

04:26.767 --> 04:30.771
Hmm. Actually,
there is one more,

04:30.804 --> 04:32.773
but I don't think
you like it.

04:32.806 --> 04:35.175
What?
I am 100% into this.

04:35.208 --> 04:37.144
Please. Give it to me!

04:37.177 --> 04:39.680
Hmm, okay.

04:39.713 --> 04:43.283
But $20 extra charge.
No refund. Thank you.

04:43.317 --> 04:44.452
Okay. Whatever.

04:44.485 --> 04:45.919
Follow me, please.

04:45.953 --> 04:48.422
Whoo-hoo-hoo!
Should I cover my eyes?

04:48.456 --> 04:50.458
[ Chuckling ] Ohh.

04:50.491 --> 04:54.795
Mr. Park?
[ Speaking Korean ]

04:54.828 --> 04:56.497
Whoa.

04:58.031 --> 05:01.335
Hello. Welcome to
Korean body scrub time.

05:01.369 --> 05:05.005
Ah! Korean body scrub time.
I'm into that. [ Giggles ]

05:05.038 --> 05:06.340
[ Grunts ]

05:06.374 --> 05:08.342
Scrub my body, please.

05:08.376 --> 05:10.177
Okay. Let's go.

05:10.210 --> 05:12.846
Aja! Ajajajaja!

05:12.880 --> 05:14.948
Wait. What are you doing?
No, no, no, no!

05:14.982 --> 05:16.817
No, no, no, no, no, no!
Aah!

05:16.850 --> 05:20.320
-Korean candy.
-[ Groans ]

05:20.354 --> 05:21.522
Uh, excuse me.

05:21.555 --> 05:23.657
No, no, no, no, no.

05:23.691 --> 05:26.360
No, no, I already ate, man.
No.

05:26.394 --> 05:28.662
[ Groans ]
Personal space.

05:28.696 --> 05:30.831
[ Speaking Korean ]

05:30.864 --> 05:33.333
Okay, I think I had enough
steam. It was a pleasure, sir.

05:33.367 --> 05:36.537
Hmm. What the...? Hmm.

05:36.570 --> 05:39.507
[ Grunting ]

05:39.540 --> 05:41.809
-Uh.
-Wha--?

05:41.842 --> 05:43.343
Ugh, why me?

05:43.377 --> 05:44.912
[ Ping-Pong balls bouncing
rapidly ]

05:44.945 --> 05:47.381
Geez, can you believe
this guy?

05:47.415 --> 05:49.517
This is his first time
playing.

05:54.388 --> 05:56.023
[ Gasps ]

05:58.258 --> 05:59.893
Hmm.

05:59.927 --> 06:02.396
Ahh!
Okay, too aggressive.

06:02.430 --> 06:04.832
Ah.
Yo yo ma. Yo yo ma.

06:04.865 --> 06:06.734
Ahh!
I want that fur to stay.

06:06.767 --> 06:09.503
Oh, man,
how is this helping anyone?

06:09.537 --> 06:11.238
[ Elevator dings ]

06:11.271 --> 06:13.674
[ Groans, grunts ]

06:13.707 --> 06:14.942
Oh, my skin.

06:14.975 --> 06:16.544
Ugh.
I gotta get out of here.

06:16.577 --> 06:19.012
-Hello.
-Aah! No more, please.

06:19.046 --> 06:20.881
Thank you for coming
to Hill Spa.

06:20.914 --> 06:24.017
Please pay now.
Cash or credit card?

06:24.051 --> 06:26.253
Oh, okay.
Well, I have this coupon.

06:26.286 --> 06:27.955
It should cover it all.

06:27.988 --> 06:30.724
Hmm. This is not
a Hill Spa coupon.

06:30.758 --> 06:32.860
What? I mean, I know it's got
some stains on there,

06:32.893 --> 06:36.396
but [blows] it's still good.
See? [ Gasp ]

06:36.430 --> 06:39.399
"Bill's Spa"?

06:39.433 --> 06:41.301
Cash or credit card,
please?

06:41.334 --> 06:44.071
Oh, well, uh, I guess
there's been a little mistake,

06:44.104 --> 06:45.873
but maybe I can find
a real coupon.

06:45.906 --> 06:47.575
I'm just going to go check
the garbage outside.

06:47.608 --> 06:49.076
-[ Grunts ]
-Ah-ha.

06:49.109 --> 06:52.580
You are not going
anywhere.

06:52.613 --> 06:54.615
[ Chuckles ]

06:55.449 --> 06:56.984
Help! Help! Please!

06:57.017 --> 06:58.552
Please, help!
The door is stuck!

06:58.586 --> 07:00.253
Oh, man, it's too hot.

07:00.287 --> 07:01.555
Maybe I can turn it down.

07:01.589 --> 07:02.923
Uh, maybe this button...?

07:02.956 --> 07:04.458
[ Woman speaking Korean ]
Or, no.

07:04.492 --> 07:05.626
Uh, this button?

07:05.659 --> 07:07.427
[ Woman speaking Korean ]

07:07.461 --> 07:10.564
Ah, I can't understand
this, I can't read Korean.

07:10.598 --> 07:13.000
Oh. Hey, mister,
can you read this?

07:13.033 --> 07:16.904
[ Gasps ]
-[ Speaking Korean ]

07:16.937 --> 07:18.772
Oh, no.
Sir, please wake up. Please.

07:18.806 --> 07:20.107
Oh, not good.

07:20.140 --> 07:22.910
[ Blowing ]
I gotta turn this steam down.

07:22.943 --> 07:25.646
Oh, less steam, less steam,
less steam.

07:25.679 --> 07:28.248
[ Woman speaking Korean ]
What? No.

07:28.281 --> 07:31.251
[ Speaking Korean ]

07:31.284 --> 07:32.786
Please pay! Thank you!

07:32.820 --> 07:35.255
If you don't pay,
I call police.

07:35.288 --> 07:36.624
Police. Popo.

07:36.657 --> 07:38.158
[ Imitates police siren ]
You know?

07:38.191 --> 07:40.027
Please, I'm sure
we can figure this out.

07:40.060 --> 07:41.795
Why are you
holding brother?

07:41.829 --> 07:44.464
Bro, you gotta help me.
They're gonna body-scrub me.

07:44.498 --> 07:45.733
Mm.

07:47.668 --> 07:50.671
You.
I saw you play Ping-Pong.

07:50.704 --> 07:54.508
You think you are good Ping-Pong
player, hmm? Ice Bear dabbles.

07:54.542 --> 07:59.880
You think you're good, but I am
Korean Ping-Pong super master.

07:59.913 --> 08:01.481
Ahh!

08:01.515 --> 08:04.284
So I have a solution
to this.

08:04.317 --> 08:05.686
Here is the deal.

08:05.719 --> 08:07.655
You play Ping-Pong with me.

08:07.688 --> 08:10.057
If you win,
brown bear can go home.

08:10.090 --> 08:15.228
But if you lose, I call police
and brown bear go to jail.

08:15.262 --> 08:16.664
Okay?

08:17.698 --> 08:20.634
-Ice Bear accepts.
-[ Laughs ] Mr. Choi.

08:20.668 --> 08:22.703
[ Speaking Korean ]

08:22.736 --> 08:31.244
♪♪

08:31.278 --> 08:32.780
[ Whimpers ]

08:38.085 --> 08:40.287
[ Grunting ]

08:44.424 --> 08:46.159
[ Whimpers ] Ow.

08:46.193 --> 08:52.532
♪♪

08:52.566 --> 08:54.668
Panda: Too much steam.

08:54.702 --> 08:56.036
There's too much steam.

08:56.069 --> 08:57.404
[ Glass shatters ]
Huh?

09:00.040 --> 09:03.410
Oh. Yeah. Oh. Ahh. Oh.

09:07.114 --> 09:08.816
[ Chuckles ]

09:09.750 --> 09:11.084
Match point!

09:11.118 --> 09:13.020
[ Hissing ]

09:13.053 --> 09:16.023
Maybe if I mess
with these buttons,

09:16.056 --> 09:18.959
the steam's pressure
will get us out of here.

09:18.992 --> 09:20.628
[ Woman speaking Korean ]

09:20.661 --> 09:22.395
Aha. I think that did it.

09:22.429 --> 09:24.364
Don't worry.
I'll get us out of here, sir.

09:24.397 --> 09:26.967
Try not to breathe too heavy.
Stay calm.

09:27.000 --> 09:29.102
[ Woman speaking Korean ]

09:31.271 --> 09:32.773
Mm.

09:35.142 --> 09:36.309
Ha!

09:37.745 --> 09:39.412
[ Speaking Korean,
coughing ]

09:39.446 --> 09:40.914
Huh?

09:45.452 --> 09:47.721
I am true master.

09:47.755 --> 09:49.322
[ Explosion ]

09:49.356 --> 09:51.825
[ All coughing ]

09:51.859 --> 09:54.795
[ Speaking Korean ]

09:55.763 --> 09:57.597
Help! Please help!

09:57.631 --> 09:59.599
This old guy needs help.
Please help him.

09:59.633 --> 10:01.468
[ Groaning ]

10:01.501 --> 10:04.604
[ Gasps,
speaking Korean ]

10:04.638 --> 10:07.307
[ Conversing in Korean ]

10:12.512 --> 10:14.481
-What did he say?
-Thank you!

10:14.514 --> 10:16.449
You save my father.

10:16.483 --> 10:18.451
I need to give you reward.

10:18.485 --> 10:21.354
No, that's okay, really.
I'm just happy to help.

10:21.388 --> 10:23.824
Uh, maybe you could let me go?
Please?

10:23.857 --> 10:27.160
Oh, yes,
brown bear is your friend.

10:27.194 --> 10:29.963
Okay, then he don't need
to pay today. Okay?

10:29.997 --> 10:33.967
Oh, thank you.
Thank you so much. Hands off.

10:34.001 --> 10:36.970
Ah. You saved us, Panda.
And that old Korean guy.

10:37.004 --> 10:39.973
Ice Bear had nothing at stake.
Mostly just showing off.

10:40.007 --> 10:42.142
Don't mention it, fellas.
I just wish

10:42.175 --> 10:44.644
we could've had a normal
relaxing day at the spa.

10:44.678 --> 10:47.314
Too bad I don't have
a real coupon for this place.

10:47.347 --> 10:50.017
[ Speaking Korean ]

10:51.819 --> 10:55.388
For you,
free pass everything, okay?

10:55.422 --> 10:58.058
[ Snoring ]

10:59.592 --> 11:01.494
Eh.

11:01.528 --> 11:04.164
Mm. Hmm.
Pretty good.

11:06.266 --> 11:14.241
♪♪

11:14.274 --> 11:22.582
